## Definition of Ready for Build

- Scrape run complete with all URLs extracted.
- URL inventory finalized and keyword-assigned.
- Content specifications approved for batch page types.
- Unique content audit complete for batch pages.
- Strapi model fit reviewed and gaps logged.

## Definition of Done for Migration

- All included pages live with optimized content following specifications.
- Metadata optimized per Keyword Strategy guidelines.
- Internal links preserved for high-value pathways.
- FAQs structured with FAQ schema markup.
- NL/EN routing parity correct.
- Technical SEO validated (canonical, hreflang, robots).
- Post-launch monitoring plan active.
- Performance baseline documented for comparison.
